        <p class="buyer-card__body">The most-searched accounting question among U.S. small business owners. A definitional comparison of scope, credentials, pricing, and when each is needed &mdash; most businesses need both, and the page explains how the two roles coordinate.</p><a class="buyer-card__cta" href="/vs/bookkeeper-vs-accountant/">Read Bookkeeper vs Accountant &rarr;</a>
