{# ── BUYER-CARD · QuickBooks vs alternatives grid (from /quickbooks/compare/ qb-compare-hub-vs-alternatives) ── #}
<section class="section" id="kitchen-sink-c1-comparison-hub-vs-alternatives">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="section__header">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">QuickBooks vs alternatives</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading">QuickBooks against the other tools.</h2><p class="section__lede">Five honest, side-by-side reads. We prefer QuickBooks and we say so &mdash; but where one of these fits your business better, we name it.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <article class="buyer-card">
        <h3 class="buyer-card__heading">QuickBooks vs Xero</h3>
        <p class="buyer-card__body">The closest head-to-head. Xero is a genuinely strong double-entry cloud platform with clean multi-currency &mdash; we tell you the kinds of businesses where it&rsquo;s the better call, and where QuickBooks&rsquo; ecosystem and ProAdvisor depth win.</p>
        <a class="buyer-card__cta" href="/quickbooks/compare/quickbooks-vs-xero/">QuickBooks vs Xero &rarr;</a>
