          <p>Yes &mdash; and we disclose it. We&rsquo;re an independent Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm, so QuickBooks is what we specialize in and what we prefer. We&rsquo;re upfront about that rather than pretending to be neutral. But preference isn&rsquo;t the same as dishonesty: these comparisons are written to be fair, with each competitor&rsquo;s real strengths described accurately, and we name the cases where another tool is genuinely the better fit for your business. We are not affiliated with Xero, Wave, Sage, FreshBooks, or Zoho.</p>
