        </h3>
        <div class="faq__answer" id="kitchen-sink-c1-comparison-hub-faq-a2" data-open="false">
          <p>There isn&rsquo;t one answer &mdash; it depends on fit. The &ldquo;best&rdquo; software is the one that matches how your business actually works: your size, industry, whether you carry inventory or run projects, whether you need an accountant network, and how you want to grow. A free invoicing-first tool can be perfect for a solo freelancer and completely wrong for a growing product company. That&rsquo;s why each comparison is framed around fit, not a universal winner. If you want a straight read on your situation, start with a free file review.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
